Class BloomFilterStatistic

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.api.Statistic<V>

        • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.statistics.field.BloomFilterStatistic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Persistable

    public class BloomFilterStatistic
extends FieldStatistic<BloomFilterStatistic.BloomFilterValue>
    Applies a bloom filter to field values useful for quickly determining set membership. False positives are possible but false negatives are not possible. In other words, a value can be determined to be possibly in the set or definitely not in the set.
